RESEARCH ACKNOWLEDGMENTS

This work builds upon and extends research from various institutions and
academic publications. We acknowledge the following research contributions:

Mixture of Experts Literature:
- Original Mixture of Experts work by Jacobs et al. (1991)
- Switch Transformer architecture by Fedus et al. (2021)
- GLaM architecture by Du et al. (2021)

Parameter-Efficient Fine-Tuning:
- LoRA methodology by Hu et al. (2021)
- AdaLoRA by Zhang et al. (2023)
- Parallel adapter architectures

Constitutional AI and Safety:
- Constitutional AI by Anthropic (Bai et al., 2022)
- Safety evaluation methodologies

Statistical Methodology:
- Bootstrap methodology by Efron & Tibshirani
- Multiple testing corrections by Benjamini & Hochberg
- Effect size analysis frameworks

