DATASET ACKNOWLEDGMENTS

This software may be used with various datasets. Users should ensure proper
attribution and compliance with dataset licenses when using BEM with specific
datasets. Common datasets that may be used include:

- Common Crawl data (subject to Common Crawl Terms of Use)
- Various academic benchmarks (each with their own licensing terms)
- OpenAI datasets (subject to OpenAI's usage policies)

Users are responsible for ensuring compliance with all applicable dataset
licenses and terms of use.

